media: coda: V4L2_PIX_FMT_GREY for coda960 JPEG Encoder

support greyscale pix fmt input for coda9_jpeg_encoder. The hardware
supports it, so allow V4L2 Mem2Mem JPEG Encoder use it as well. Tested
on an i.MX6QP.

